## Table Schemas & Column Descriptions

### 1. olist_orders_dataset (Core Table)
| Column | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `order_id` | Unique identifier for each order |
| `customer_id` | Unique identifier for each customer |
| `order_status` | Status of the order (delivered, cancelled, shipped, etc.) |
| `order_purchase_timestamp` | Date and time of order purchase |
| `order_approved_at` | Approval date and time |
| `order_delivered_customer_date` | Date and time of delivery to customer |
| `order_estimated_delivery_date` | Estimated delivery date |

